items.title: Chan's algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Chan's algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
In the planar case, the algorithm combines an O(n log n) algorithm (Graham scan
, for example) with Jarvis march, in order to obtain an optimal O(n log h) time.
